message.body: Hey Jim. My move is taking longer than expected. I expect to be finished by tonight, but I won't be able to return the keys until tomorrow. Is that all right?
Jim, I came by the office just now to drop the keys off, but no one was available. I'll try again tomorrow.
U can drop them in the nail slot with a note to identify them. Thanks.
Dropped them in. They're wrapped in plastic with a note.
Thanks for having me as a resident. I'll contact you later this month to discuss the security deposit.
We enjoyed your being here, John. Best wishes!
